name: Skyflow Detect Connector
description: De-identify and re-identify sensitive data via Skyflow Detect APIs

properties.label: Vault URI
properties.description: The subdomain/identifier of your vault (e.g. ebfc9bee4242)

properties.label: Payload
properties.description: FEEL expression evaluating to a JSON object with data to process. Example: { name: name, age: age }

properties.label: Token type
properties.description: Type of tokens to generate during de-identification (only applies to DEIDENTIFY operation)

properties.label: Entity types
properties.description: Optional FEEL expression resolving to a list of entity types to de-identify (strings). Example: ["EMAIL", "PHONE_NUMBER"]. If omitted/empty, Skyflow will de-identify all supported entities.

properties.label: Result variable
properties.description: Name of variable to store the response in

properties.label: Result expression
properties.description: Expression to map the response into process variables

properties.label: Error expression
properties.description: Expression to handle errors. Details in the documentation.

properties.label: Retry backoff
properties.description: ISO-8601 duration to wait between retries
